# Development Workflow

## General Guidelines
- Follow user requirements carefully & to the letter
- Think step-by-step before coding
- Write correct, bug-free, fully functional code
- Focus on readability over performance
- Leave NO todos or placeholders
- Be concise

## Development Process
- Use SwiftUI previews for rapid iteration
- Follow Git branching strategy
- Write descriptive commit messages
- Review code before merging
- Aim for high test coverage

## Dependencies
- Prefer Swift Package Manager
- Keep dependencies up to date
- Document why dependencies are needed

## Testing
- Test on multiple device sizes
- Verify different network conditions
- Test with accessibility features enabled
